1	/**
2	 * LayerInfinite MCP Server — tools/li-observe.ts
3	 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
4	 * Always registered. Returns per-task outcome statistics.
5	 * Maps to GET /v1/observe?task={task} on the LI REST API.
